headline.print_headline: Halep Pays Heavy Price for Beating Williams
headline.main: Halep Pays Heavy Price for Beating Williams

lead_paragraph: Simona Halep, like many others before her, learnt a hard lesson on Sunday, that there is a hefty price to pay for beating Serena Williams.
